crash.df <- read.csv("crash.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",")

#View(crash.df)

#fix bad column value
crash.df$Drug.Involvement[crash.df$Drug.Involvement == "\\N"] <- "Not Reported"
crash.df$Roadway[crash.df$Roadway == "\\N"] <- "Rural-Local Road or Street"
#Fix 'NA' in numeric column alcohol, change to -100 so is not grouped with actual readings
crash.df$Alcohol.Results <- ifelse(is.na(crash.df$Alcohol.Results), -100, crash.df$Alcohol.Results) 
#Fix 'NA' in numeric column Age
ave_age <- ave(crash.df$Age, crash.df$State, FUN = function(x) mean(x, na.rm = TRUE))
#help(ave)
#ave_age
crash.df$Age <- ifelse(is.na(crash.df$Age), round(ave_age, digits = 0), crash.df$Age) 


#crash.df$Atmospheric.Condition <- as.numeric(crash.df$Atmospheric.Condition)
#crash.df$State.Numeric <- as.numeric(crash.df$State)
#crash.df$Roadway <- as.numeric(crash.df$Roadway)
#crash.df$Gender <- as.numeric(crash.df$Gender)
#crash.df$Injury.Severity <- as.numeric(crash.df$Injury.Severity)
#crash.df$Drug.Involvement <- as.numeric(crash.df$Drug.Involvement)
crash.df <- crash.df[,-c(10)] # drop Race column


#View(crash.df)

#is.na(crash.df)
#is.infinite(crash.df$Atmospheric.Condition)
crash.df[rowSums(is.na(crash.df)) > 0,]
